videos.description: Oklahoma QB Baker Mayfield gets picked off by Texas DB Dylan Haines at midfield, giving Texas its first interception of the season.
videos.headline: Texas picks off Mayfield for first interception of season

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas picks off Mayfield for first interception of season) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma RB Samaje Perine forces his way into the end zone, giving the Sooners a short-lived lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Perine's 2-yard run gives Oklahoma a short-lived lead

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perine's 2-yard run gives Oklahoma the lead) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.description: Texas RB D'Onta Foreman runs the ball into the end zone from one yard out, giving the Longhorns the lead back from Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Texas strikes with D'Onta Foreman 1-yard TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas strikes with D'Onta Foreman 1-yard TD) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma QB Baker Mayfield scrambles and finds Dede Westbrook open downfield for a 71-yard touchdown strike, giving the Sooners the lead back over Texas.
videos.headline: Mayfield launches 71-yard touchdown pass

videos.description: Texas QB Shane Buechele perfectly drops a pass in for Devin Duvernay, who scores a 63-yard touchdown to give the Sooners the lead at the start of the second half.
videos.headline: Buechele finds Duvernay for 63-yard touchdown pass

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buechele finds Duvernay for 63-yard touchdown pass) 2016/10/8 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma QB Baker Mayfield finds Dede Westbrook for their second touchdown connection of the game to give the Sooners the lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Westbrook strikes again with 42-yard touchdown grab

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Westbrook strikes again with 42-yard touchdown grab) 2016/10/8 ESHEET

videos.description: Texas QB Shane Buechele launches a ball that is brilliantly caught by Dorian Leonard for a 45-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Texas WR Leonard hauls in 45-yard touchdown grab

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas WR Leonard hauls in 45-yard touchdown grab) 2016/10/8 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma QB Baker Mayfield re-gains the lead for the Sooners after finding his way into the end zone for a 4-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Mayfield rushes four yards for score

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mayfield rushes four yards for score) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma QB Baker Mayfield scores his fourth touchdown of the game against Texas, and third to Dede Westbrook, this one a 47-yard strike to put Oklahoma up 35-27 on Texas.
videos.headline: Mayfield-Westbrook connection fuels Oklahoma in win

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mayfield hits Westbrook for third TD of game) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma WR Dede Westbrook broke the school's single-game record for receiving yards on a 71-yard touchdown Saturday against Texas. Sooners QB Baker Mayfield and Longhorns coach Charlie Strong discuss the play that broke open the Red River Showdown.
videos.headline: Dede Westbrook's record-setting TD lifts OU

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Feature (Inside the Play: Oklahoma def Texas) 2016/10/08 ODV
